00:05:10.280 --> 00:05:16.920
unbound, you can actually say this post-process should impact the entire world if you wanted

77
00:05:16.920 --> 00:05:17.920
to.

78
00:05:17.920 --> 00:05:18.920
So have a play around with post-processing.

